00:00:00,672 --> 00:00:12,730
[SPEAKER_00]: Um, all right on March 29th, 2023 governor Healy signed into law a supplemental budget bill, which, among other things, extends the temporary provisions pertaining to the open meeting law to March 31st, 2025 specifically this further extension.

